{
  "stem": "56.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And my dad, in turn, decided that, since we were all going to be working, he felt that someone should keep the family together.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the only way to keep the families together, if there's someone going to be in charge of the family.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So my dad decided that he's going to be a janitor.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And by being a janitor in the building [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] next to our little house, he'll be home all the time.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He'll do his work, and he'll be home.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when he's home, he can do some laundry or he can do some cooking-- because we used to get a ration of food, by then.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We used to get a couple of potatoes, or everybody got a piece of bread that we used to take it as one bread.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this way, have a little warm tea or something when you come home from work.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this worked out pretty good, because we never came to an empty house.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We always came to a house that was a home-- not like everybody that I knew came into a cold, empty house.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So-- and also, it gave him an opportunity, while he was home alone, to invite a lot of people who did not work for one reason or another.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there were always people-- especially young people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "All my friends, my sister's friends, my brother's friends knew that this was at home that you can come into and get away from your problems, because my father used to put on shows, used to teach them songs and dancing.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he always used to say, this will pass.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You have to have hope.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "This will pass.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we have to study, and we have to learn, and we have to be happy.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
